The All Progressives Congress (APC) National Working Committee (NWC), has announced the lifting of suspension of the Deputy National Chairman (North), Shuaibu Lawal and National Vice Chairman (North-west), Abdulkadir Inuwa. This was after it rose from several hours meeting at the party’s National Secretariat. The NWC also resolved to withdraw all pending cases in the court of law instituted by any of the national officers against each other.